  <summary date="2021-04-06T00:18:07Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Pandemic Heroes Compensation Act of 2021

This bill allows essential workers and their family members to file claims and receive compensation for harm or death suffered as a result of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019).

A Special Master appointed by the Department of Justice must review claims submitted and determine if a claimant&#160;is eligible for compensation, the extent of the harm to the claimant, and the amount of compensation to be awarded.</summary>
